---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro'
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro'
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro'
import { t } from '../../i18n/translations'
const locale = 'en'
const tr = t(locale)
---
<Base title="How we work" description="Our strength lies in combining research, design and realisation." locale={locale} altHref="/hoe">
  <Nav locale={locale} altHref="/hoe" activePage="hoe" />

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="bg-creme pt-[88px] pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-content mx-auto px-10">
      <span class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-green pb-2 border-b-2 border-green inline-block mb-5">How we work</span>
      <h1 class="text-[clamp(36px,4.5vw,58px)] font-bold leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.025em] text-green text-balance mb-5">How we work</h1>
      <p class="text-[18px] text-mid leading-[1.75] max-w-[680px]">Our strength lies in combining research, design and realisation. We are researcher, designer, facilitator and project manager in one. With us you get not only a sharp vision but also the concrete translation and practical execution.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-content mx-auto px-10">

      <!-- Phase 1 -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-[96px_1fr_1fr] gap-10 py-14 border-b border-border items-start">
        <div class="text-[72px] font-extrabold text-magenta leading-none">#1</div>
        <div>
          <span class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-green pb-2 border-b-2 border-green inline-block mb-3">Phase one</span>
          <h3 class="text-[28px] font-bold text-green leading-snug mb-2.5">Research & Strategy</h3>
          <p class="text-[15px] text-mid leading-[1.75] mb-4">Complex questions brought to their core and translated into ideas & concrete strategies.</p>
          <p class="text-[15px] text-mid leading-[1.75] mb-4">Every transition begins with a new narrative: a vision of the future firmly anchored in the present. Together with partners we investigate complex issues and bring them back to their core. We always look at systems as a whole and from all perspectives: of people and nature alike.</p>
          <p class="text-[15px] text-mid leading-[1.75] mb-4">We analyse trends and identify opportunities for innovation. We provide strategies that turn new ideas into concrete results.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3.5">
            <span class="text-[12px] font-semibold px-3.5 py-[5px] rounded-pill border-[1.5px] border-green text-green">Systems analysis</span>
            <span class="text-[12px] font-semibold px-3.5 py-[5px] rounded-pill border-[1.5px] border-green text-green">Trend research</span>
            <span class="text-[12px] font-semibold px-3.5 py-[5px] rounded-pill border-[1.5px] border-green text-green">Stakeholder research</span>
            <span class="text-[12px] font-semibold px-3.5 py-[5px] rounded-pill border-[1.5px] border-green text-green">Strategy formation</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6">
            <a href="/en/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[14px] font-semibold text-green before:content-['>'] hover:text-magenta transition-colors">Research together?</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <div class="bg-creme rounded-lg p-5">
            <div class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-light mb-1.5">Example project</div>
            <div class="text-[14px] font-bold text-green mb-1.5">Amsterdam Regenerative City</div>
            <p class="text-[12px] text-mid leading-[1.55]">Research and vision development for the City of Amsterdam into the city as a regenerative ecosystem. Resulted in design principles, models and policy proposals.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-creme rounded-lg p-5">
            <div class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-light mb-1.5">Example project</div>
            <div class="text-[14px] font-bold text-green mb-1.5">Amsterdam Smart City</div>
            <p class="text-[12px] text-mid leading-[1.55]">User research, data analysis and a new proposition and platform concept for a renewed Amsterdam Smart City platform.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 2 -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-[96px_1fr_1fr] gap-10 py-14 border-b border-border items-start">
        <div class="text-[72px] font-extrabold text-magenta leading-none">#2</div>
        <div>
          <span class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-green pb-2 border-b-2 border-green inline-block mb-3">Phase two</span>
          <h3 class="text-[28px] font-bold text-green leading-snug mb-2.5">Concept & Design</h3>
          <p class="text-[15px] text-mid leading-[1.75] mb-4">Innovative concepts, systems and places that shape the regenerative society.</p>
          <p class="text-[15px] text-mid leading-[1.75] mb-4">As a creative studio we design regenerative concepts: from digital services to spatial interventions. For us there is no separation between the physical and digital domain — both are needed in the transition to a new narrative. Technology is never a goal in itself, but a means.</p>
          <p class="text-[15px] text-mid leading-[1.75] mb-4">In our toolkit we combine regenerative methods such as permaculture, systems thinking and biobased design with innovation techniques such as design thinking and lean startup.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3.5">
            <span class="text-[12px] font-semibold px-3.5 py-[5px] rounded-pill border-[1.5px] border-green text-green">Design thinking</span>
            <span class="text-[12px] font-semibold px-3.5 py-[5px] rounded-pill border-[1.5px] border-green text-green">Spatial design</span>
            <span class="text-[12px] font-semibold px-3.5 py-[5px] rounded-pill border-[1.5px] border-green text-green">Business models</span>
            <span class="text-[12px] font-semibold px-3.5 py-[5px] rounded-pill border-[1.5px] border-green text-green">Digital services</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6">
            <a href="/en/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[14px] font-semibold text-green before:content-['>'] hover:text-magenta transition-colors">Collaborate?</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <div class="bg-creme rounded-lg p-5">
            <div class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-light mb-1.5">Example project</div>
            <div class="text-[14px] font-bold text-green mb-1.5">Taralena Retreat Center</div>
            <p class="text-[12px] text-mid leading-[1.55]">A first design vision for a holistic centre dedicated to healing, education and community building. Integral Theory and regenerative principles translated into architectural design.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-creme rounded-lg p-5">
            <div class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-light mb-1.5">Example project</div>
            <div class="text-[14px] font-bold text-green mb-1.5">Broad Prosperity Meter</div>
            <p class="text-[12px] text-mid leading-[1.55]">In a design sprint, a prototype app was developed together with the City of Amsterdam. The app lets civil servants reflect on their work in relation to broad prosperity through statements.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 3 -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-[96px_1fr_1fr] gap-10 py-14 items-start">
        <div class="text-[72px] font-extrabold text-magenta leading-none">#3</div>
        <div>
          <span class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-green pb-2 border-b-2 border-green inline-block mb-3">Phase three</span>
          <h3 class="text-[28px] font-bold text-green leading-snug mb-2.5">Co-creation & Realisation</h3>
          <p class="text-[15px] text-mid leading-[1.75] mb-4">Guiding groups and organisations in co-creation, both in vision and concept and in execution.</p>
          <p class="text-[15px] text-mid leading-[1.75] mb-4">In a fragmented and complex world we focus attention on what truly matters. We guide groups and organisations in co-creation, with interactive and experiential working methods that activate collective creative power.</p>
          <p class="text-[15px] text-mid leading-[1.75] mb-4">We translate vision and concept into concrete programmes and projects. We form coalitions and work together with a broad network of partners.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3.5">
            <span class="text-[12px] font-semibold px-3.5 py-[5px] rounded-pill border-[1.5px] border-green text-green">Co-creation</span>
            <span class="text-[12px] font-semibold px-3.5 py-[5px] rounded-pill border-[1.5px] border-green text-green">Labs & Pilots</span>
            <span class="text-[12px] font-semibold px-3.5 py-[5px] rounded-pill border-[1.5px] border-green text-green">Partnerships</span>
            <span class="text-[12px] font-semibold px-3.5 py-[5px] rounded-pill border-[1.5px] border-green text-green">Team building</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6">
            <a href="/en/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[14px] font-semibold text-green before:content-['>'] hover:text-magenta transition-colors">Co-create?</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <div class="bg-creme rounded-lg p-5">
            <div class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-light mb-1.5">Example project</div>
            <div class="text-[14px] font-bold text-green mb-1.5">Oosterwold in Abundance</div>
            <p class="text-[12px] text-mid leading-[1.55]">A area workshop in Almere Oosterwold where residents, farmers, officials and developers came together to explore new forms of cooperation.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-creme rounded-lg p-5">
            <div class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-light mb-1.5">Example project</div>
            <div class="text-[14px] font-bold text-green mb-1.5">Broad Prosperity Scan</div>
            <p class="text-[12px] text-mid leading-[1.55]">An instrument to comprehensively assess the effects of policy proposals on ten themes of broad prosperity, now and in the future.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer locale={locale} />
</Base>
